bilingual.source: His dependence on coffee is becoming a problem.
bilingual.target: 他对咖啡的依赖正在成为一个问题。

bilingual.source: Nuclear energy can reduce dependence on fossil fuels.
bilingual.target: 核能可以减少对化石燃料的依赖。

bilingual.source: Biomass fuel can reduce dependence on fossil fuels.
bilingual.target: 生物质燃料可以减少对化石燃料的依赖。

bilingual.source: Using biofuel helps reduce dependence on fossil fuels.
bilingual.target: 使用生物燃料有助于减少对化石燃料的依赖。

bilingual.source: The country's dependence on foreign oil is a major concern.
bilingual.target: 该国对外国石油的依赖是一个主要的担忧。

bilingual.source: The project failed due to its dependence on outdated technology.
bilingual.target: 由于对过时技术的依赖，项目失败了。

bilingual.source: Reducing dependence on plastic is crucial for environmental health.
bilingual.target: 减少对塑料的依赖对环境健康至关重要。

bilingual.source: Austen's works often explore the dependence of women on marriage.
bilingual.target: 奥斯汀的作品经常探讨女性对婚姻的依赖。

bilingual.source: He is trying to get rid of dependence on his parents.
bilingual.target: 他努力摆脱依赖父母的生活。

bilingual.source: She has a strong dependence on her family for emotional support.
bilingual.target: 她在情感支持上对家人的依赖很强。

yingyinNormal.en: Manufacturing has grown. Our deficits have shrunk. Our dependence on foreign oil is down. Clean energy is up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 制造业在蓬勃发展，我们的赤字已经削减了，我们对国外石油的依赖在下降，清洁能源在发展。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
